                <div class="rendering rendering_researchoutput  rendering_researchoutput_apa rendering_contributiontojournal rendering_apa rendering_contributiontojournal_apa">Xu, Y., Cawood, P., Du, Y., Zhong, Z., &amp; Hughes, N. C. (2014). <a rel="ContributionToJournal" href="https://research-repository.uwa.edu.au/en/publications/terminal-suturing-of-gondwana-along-the-southern-margin-of-south-/" class="link"><span>Terminal suturing of Gondwana along the southern margin of South China Craton: Evidence from detrital zircon U-Pb ages and Hf isotopes in Cambrian and Ordovician strata, Hainan Island</span></a>. <a rel="Journal" href="#" class="link"><span><em>Tectonics</em></span></a>, <em>33</em>(12), 2490-2504. <a onclick="window.open(this.href, '_blank','noopener,noreferrer'); return false;" href="https://doi.org/10.1002/2014TC003748" class="link"><span>https://doi.org/10.1002/2014TC003748</span></a></div>
